    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition, having been meticulously preserved by its previous owner. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior is pristine, smelling and looking as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, it is perfect, offering a driving experience that is smooth, powerful, and entirely free of any issues. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that needs absolutely nothing.",
